scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The collection consists of videotape masters of SCBN programming, PSAs, and advertisements on a variety of topics.

bioghist.head: Biographical/Historical note
bioghist.p: The Stanford Cardinal Broadcasting Network (SCBN) is Stanfordâ€™s only student-run TV station. They broadcast to every residence and public television on campus. As a student and public access TV station, their goal is to provide the Stanford community with innovative, original, and targeted programming.

As a club, SCBN supports original shows and student filmmakers. SCBN also teaches a Production Workshop for those who are interested in TV Production and want to learn more. SCBN broadcasts programming, PSAs, and advertisements from the broader Bay Area community.
